== 儿童读物 ==
瓦龙曾创作多本儿童读物，均以英语和缅甸语出版。2015年，他创作《园丁》（''The Gardener''）一书，推动宽容、和谐、温暖社会环境的建立<ref name="Kermeliotis"/>。

在[[永盛监狱|永盛监狱]]关押期间，瓦龙创作儿童读物《记者杰杰》（''Jay Jay the Journalist''），讲述一位好奇心极强的男孩子不懈寻找村庄的植物和动物凋亡真相的过程，借此“鼓励孩子们学习批判性思维，并向他们介绍记者一职”<ref name="Kermeliotis"/>。“第三故事计划”的主任Ei Pwint Rhi Zan受委托负责该书的发行，该组织以向缅甸弱势儿童制作和分发免费书籍为使命<ref name="Kermeliotis"/>，于2014年7月在瓦龙的协助下成立<ref name="Kermeliotis"/><ref name="booklovers"/>。《杰杰》系列的第二部作品设有一位强大的女主角，目前正在创作中<ref name="Kermeliotis"/><ref name="Sing">{{cite news |last1=Lee |first1=Sing |title=Turning the page with a new generation of children’s books |url=https://frontiermyanmar.net/en/turning-the-page-with-a-new-generation-of-childrens-books |accessdate=2018-12-25 |work=Frontier (Myanmar) |date=2017-08-22 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103141324/https://www.frontiermyanmar.net/en/turning-the-page-with-a-new-generation-of-childrens-books/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 家庭 ==
瓦龙服刑时，妻子潘爱蒙成了他和外部世界沟通的中介。两人的首个孩子于2018年8月出生<ref name="Kermeliotis">{{cite news |last1=Kermeliotis |first1=Teo |title=From Myanmar jail, Wa Lone pens children's book on exposing truth |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/12/myanmar-jail-wa-lone-pens-children-book-exposing-truth-181211233617965.html |accessdate=2018-12-25 |work=Al Jazeera |date=2018-12-11 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103141504/https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2018/12/12/from-myanmar-jail-wa-lone-pens-childrens-book-on-exposing-truth |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Goldberg">{{cite news |last1=Goldberg |first1=Jacob |title='I struggle without him': wife of jailed Reuters reporter marks grim milestone |url=https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2018/dec/12/myanmar-wa-lone-wife-reuters-reporter-anniversary-baby |accessdate=2018-12-25 |work=The Guardian |date=2018-12-11 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103141324/https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2018/dec/12/myanmar-wa-lone-wife-reuters-reporter-anniversary-baby |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她和觉梭的妻子温琦苏自丈夫被捕之时起，频繁受到骚扰<ref name="Vick"/><ref name="Barron">{{cite news |last1=Barron |first1=Laignee |title='Please Have Mercy.' The Wives of Reuters Journalists Jailed in Myanmar Speak Out |url=http://time.com/5475493/reuters-journalists-wives-person-of-the-year-2018/ |accessdate=2018-12-25 |work=Time |date=2018-12-11 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103141323/https://time.com/5475493/reuters-journalists-wives-person-of-the-year-2018/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

